---
import BaseHead from "../components/BaseHead.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import Cover from "../components/Cover.astro";
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from "../consts";
import "../base.css";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <Cover />

    <section
      class="flex flex-col gap-6 items-center justify-center bg-primary text-five py-16"
    >
      <h2 class="font-bold md:text-5xl text-3xl w-3/5 text-center">
        Discover the power of the Collective
      </h2>
      <p class="w-3/5 leading-8 text-center">
        A community of entrepreneurs tackling the challenges of growing a
        business by overcoming our inner blocks, working on our mindset and
        becoming the version of ourselves most aligned with our desired
        outcomes.
      </p>
      <button type="button" class="btn-primary">Connect and grow</button>
    </section>

    <section
      class="grid grid-flow-row md:grid-cols-2 items-start bg-[url('/images/flowers.png')] text-primary md:p-20"
    >
      <section class="m-8 p-16 bg-primary/30 backdrop-blur-md">
        <h3 class="font-monserrat font-bold text-3xl mb-6">What If..</h3>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          the garden was the version of yourself that would best grow your
          business so you can lead life at your own terms, what flowers aka
          skills, habits, perspectives, attitudes would you grow?
        </p>
      </section>
      <section class="md:mt-32 m-8 p-16 bg-primary/30 backdrop-blur-md">
        <h3 class="font-monserrat text-3xl mb-6">
          Let’s discover it together and grow it one flower at a time!
        </h3><p class="leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Whether you're an aspiring entrepreneur or running a new or existing
          business, we’re a collective on a shared journey, figuring out ways to
          succeed on our own terms. Through deep conversations, shared learnings
          and addressing the stories we tell ourselves, we grow ourselves and
          our desired garden.
        </p><button type="button" class="btn-secondary">Connect and grow</button
        >
      </section>
    </section>

    <section class="m-12 md:m-24 gap-6 text-five">
      <header class="p-8 gap-6 justify-items-center text-center">
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-4xl">Living life on your own terms</h2>
      </header>
      <ul class="grid grid-flow-row md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-6">
        <li class="p-4">
          <img src="/images/woman.png" alt="" />
          <h3 class="font-bold font-hindlight text-2xl my-4">
            Co-create a space to grow and connect.
          </h3>
          <p class="mb-4 font-light">
            You don’t have to go through this journey alone. By joining
            EmpowerMe you become part of a collective of like-minded individuals
            who are all working towards similar goals.
          </p>
          <p class="font-light">
            This is a safe space for deep conversations, sharing perspectives
            and learnings. Grow together and find encouragement and
            accountability from peers who understand your challenges.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="p-4">
          <img src="/images/women.png" alt="" />
          <h3 class="font-bold font-hindlight text-2xl my-4">
            Fast track your journey & grow your business
          </h3>
          <p class="mb-4 font-light">
            Whether you're just starting out, are new to business or looking to
            grow it, our content is specifically designed to address the unique
            challenges faced by entrepreneurs.
          </p>
          <p class="font-light">
            We unlock challenges specific to the entrepreneurial journey through
            the lenses of the mindset and provide the tools and support you need
            to overcome any blocks holding you back from soaring high.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="p-4">
          <img src="/images/road.png" alt="" />
          <h3 class="font-bold font-hindlight text-2xl my-4">
            Align with your desired outcomes
          </h3>
          <p class="mb-4 font-light">
            The stories we tell ourselves can keep us small. By making these
            invisible blocks visible, cultivating a growth mindset and building
            empowering habits, we help you become the version of yourself that
            will take you to your desired outcomes.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-4 font-light">
            The collective offers the right environment to see right through
            these blocks, feed new perspectives and support you to grow yourself
            as a person and your business.
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
        <button type="button" class="btn-primary">Start your journey</button>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section
      class="py-16 md:px-48 gap-6 justify-items-center text-center bg-[url('/images/quote-bg.png')]
       rounded-lg"
    >
      <article class="p-16 w-full bg-primary/30 backdrop-blur-sm">
        <h3 class="font-monserrat font-bold text-3xl mb-4 text-five">
          Habits are like magic
        </h3>
        <p class="font-hindmedium md:px-44 leading-8 text-five">
          By taking action, habits become the evidence of the person we’re
          becoming which changes the way we see ourselves. And if we change how
          we view ourselves, we change what we believe is possible..
        </p>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section
      class="grid grid-flow-row md:grid-cols-2 md:p-16 p-8 gap-8 items-center justify-items-center bg-primary text-five"
    >
      <div class="md:px-8">
        <h2 class="font-monserrat font-bold text-4xl mb-8">
          This Collective is for you if ...
        </h2>
        <ul class="mb-8 list-disc pl-6 leading-8">
          <li>You want to live life on your own terms.</li>
          <li>You’re starting out or growing your business.</li>
          <li>You seek ways to grow and better yourself.</li>
          <li>You feel isolated in your entrepreneurial journey.</li>
          <li>You’re ready to take charge of your life and aspirations.</li>
        </ul>
        <section class="text-primary bg-five p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h4 class="font-bold">Disclaimer</h4>
          <p class="font-hindlight">
            This is not for you if you don't believe in your ability to change
            or take responsibility for your own growth.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
        <img
          src="/images/women.png"
          alt="Collective"
          class="rounded-3xl size-40"
        />
        <img
          src="/images/women.png"
          alt="Collective"
          class="rounded-3xl size-40"
        />
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-primary text-tenth md:p-16 p-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Take your power back</h2>
