        <section class="text-primary bg-tenth rounded-md p-4">
          <img src="/images/coffee2.png" alt="" class="rounded-md" />
          <h3 class="text-xl my-4 font-bold">Regular Meet ups</h3>
          <h4 class="font-bold mb-4">Connect, Learn, and Grow</h4>
          <p class="font-light mb-4">
            Join our in-person or online meet-ups to connect with peers, tackle
            business challenges, and share insights. These gatherings offer
            support and inspiration to help you achieve your goals and
            accelerate your journey.
          </p>
          <button class="btn-secondary">Find out more</button>
