            develop empowering habits, cultivate a growth mindset, and unlock
            your potential to achieve your goals.
          </p>
          <button class="btn-secondary">Explore the Masterclass</button>
        </section>
        <section class="text-primary bg-tenth rounded-md p-4">
          <img src="/images/flower.png" alt="" class="rounded-md" />
