                alt=""
                class="rounded-full size-16"
              />
            </div>
            <div>Tainee Marsh</div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="m-4 p-6 bg-primary rounded-md">
          <p>
            It was mind blowing for me to realise how fast we can change and how
            less stressful my life is now.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-row items-center mt-6 gap-4">
            <div>
              <img
                src="/images/Florinda.png"
                alt=""
                class="rounded-full size-16"
              />
            </div>
            <div>Florinda</div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="m-4 p-6 bg-primary rounded-md">
          <p>
            Definitely, the support has an amazing impact. [...] People around
            you invest in you and say I support your idea [...] It's I don't
            know a mixture of 'they trust me that I can do this!' So, the
            support is encouragement and also a nice push behind you :)
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-row items-center mt-6 gap-4">
            <div>
              <img
                src="/images/Sevgi.png"
                alt=""
                class="rounded-full size-16"
              />
            </div>
            <div>Sevgi</div>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <div class="flex flex-row justify-center">
        <button class="btn-secondary mt-8 mb-14">Get started today</button>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="grid grid-flow-row md:grid-cols-2 bg-primary md:p-16">
      <section class="text-five">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Upcoming events</h2>
        <p class="pt-4">Don’t miss a thing...</p>
        <p class="py-4">Missing text</p>
      </section>
      <section class="bg-five p-8 rounded-md">
        <img src="/images/sketchbook.png" alt="" class="w-48 rounded-md" />
        <h3 class="text-primary text-xl my-4">
          Don’t miss out on our upcoming events
        </h3>
        <p class="text-primary font-light">
          Join the waiting list for the regular meet ups.
        </p>
        <section class="flex my-4">
          <input
            type="text"
            class="rounded-md p-2"
            placeholder="you@example.com"
          />
          <button class="bg-secondary rounded-md p-2 ml-4 text-sm"
            >Submit</button
          >
        </section>
      </section>
    </section>

    <section class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-fourth h-96">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold md:w-2/5 w-3/4 text-center leading-loose">
        “When the student is ready, the teacher within show us”
      </h2>
      <p class="leading-loose">by Manu</p>
    </section>

    <section
      class="bg-primary text-five p-8 py-16 flex flex-col items-center justify-center"
    >
      <article class="md:w-2/4">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-8">Let me explain...</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-flow-row md:grid-cols-2 font-light gap-8 w-full">
          <p>
