          </p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section>
      <article class="text-fourth md:w-2/5 md:m-16 p-8 px-12 bg-primary">
        <h2 class="font-bold text-2xl">Our Vision</h2>
        <p class="mt-8">
          the garden was the version of yourself that would best grow your
